SetUp			cursheet

### Mesh parameters

Nx			1
Ny                	128
Nz			128
Ymin			0.0
Ymax			1.0
Zmin			0.0
Zmax			1.0

PeriodicY		yes
PeriodicZ		yes

Eta			0.0
Amplitude		0.05
Beta			0.1
Nu			0.0


Spacing			Default

### Output control parameters
Ntot			1000		Total number of time steps
Ninterm	 		5		Time steps between outputs
DT			0.05		
OutputDir		@outputs/cursheet

cmap			cubehelix
PlotLine		field[:,:,0]

